com.github.dm.jrt.retrofit

Class ProviderAdapterFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • retrofit2.CallAdapter.Factory
      • com.github.dm.jrt.retrofit.ProviderAdapterFactory

  • public class ProviderAdapterFactory
extends CallAdapter.Factory
    Implementation of a call adapter factory selecting other factory instances.
    The factory will scan the method annotations searching for CallAdapterFactory one. If found and a factory with the corresponding name has been registered, it will be employed to create the call adapter instance.
    Special factory instances can be registered to cope with the cases in which no match is found or the annotation is missing.

    Created by davide-maestroni on 05/20/2016.
